item.title: CVE-2021-29767|2024-09-17T03:02:12.396Z -- ibm -- i2%20analyst%27s%20notebook%20premium
item.description: IBM i2 Analyst's Notebook Premium 9.2.0, 9.2.1, and 9.2.2 could allow a remote attacker to obtain sensitive information when a detailed technical error message is returned in the browser. This information could be used in further attacks against the system. IBM X-Force ID: 202681.
